                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">KGV has actively enhanced my sense of belonging and self-confidence and nurtured my independent thinking and intellectual curiosity. The teachers demonstrate great compassion and foster diligent students with effective learning habits. The culture at KGV, with a focus on honesty, courage, and empathy, is shaping me into a better person.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">KGV has actively enhanced my sense of belonging and self-confidence and nurtured my independent thinking and intellectual curiosity. The teachers demonstrate great compassion and foster diligent students with effective learning habits. The culture at KGV, with a focus on honesty, courage, and empathy, is shaping me into a better person.</p>
