                        </div>
                                    </div>
                            <div class="tab-content" data-id="2">
                                            <div class="record-slider">
                            <div class="slider-container">
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/ecfbde521c46177fabdbd0772c8784c3.jpg" alt="Day 3 King George V School-83" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">As a parent of KGV, it is comforting to know my child(ren)’s teachers recognise and understand who she is, always having her best interest at heart.  We are happy to be part of this supportive community which fosters students’ academics and well-being holistically. <br><br>Proud to witness my child(ren)’s self discovery of how Remarkable they can be.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">As a parent of KGV, it is comforting to know my child(ren)’s teachers recognise and understand who she is, always having her best interest at heart.  We are happy to be part of this supportive community which fosters students’ academics and well-being holistically. <br><br>Proud to witness my child(ren)’s self discovery of how Remarkable they can be.</p>
