                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">I think being with the KGV community is one of my fondest memories. My knowledge and appreciation of different cultures and worldviews is exponentially increased due to my time at KGV.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">I think being with the KGV community is one of my fondest memories. My knowledge and appreciation of different cultures and worldviews is exponentially increased due to my time at KGV.</p>
