    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function() {
            $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').hide();
            
            $('.tab', '#section6').click(function() {
                $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $(this).addClass('current');
                $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).data('id') + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($(this).index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').addClass('current');
                chkContentHeight();
            });

            $('.tab-select', '#section6').change(function() {
                $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div:nth-child(' +  ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.select .select-container div', '#section6').show();
                $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').hide();
                chkContentHeight();
            });

            $('.record-slider', '#section6').Slider({
                slides: '.record-item',
                maxSlide: 1,
                swipeControl: true,
                skipBoundary: true,
                infiniteLoop: true
            });

            function chkContentHeight() {
                $('p.description', '#section6').each(function() {
                    if($(this).height() > 160) {
                        $(this).parent().addClass('more');
                    }
                });
            }
            chkContentHeight();

            $('.record-item article button.view-more', '#section6').click(function() {
                $(this).hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.view-less').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.description').hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.content').show();
            });
            $('.record-item article button.view-less', '#section6').click(function() {
                $(this).hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.view-more').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.description').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.content').hide();
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section7" data-total="10">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">What's new at KGV?</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="record-slider">
        <div class="slider-container">
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="257">
                        <time>27/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>The KGV stage is still cooling down! Last week, 10 student bands performed for an unforgettable night of talent and high energy. <br><br>A massive shout-out to every musician who performed—you guys made it a night to remember! Thank you to the guests for making the atmosphere electric. <br><br>Photo Credits: Huge thanks to student photographer Stephen and Ms. Carlile for capturing these epic moments!<br><br>#kgv_hk #esfschools #studentmusicians #lionrock #battleofthebands #LiveMusic</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/813df42d3801a4308bc4ff9745c4cc8b.jpg" alt="643412954_1498478428951793_5439065282363201229_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="256">
                        <time>25/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>Connecting at KGV. We recently had an insightful parent workshop on emotional resilience! We’re working together to create a harmonious environment for our students at home and at school.  For more information, KGV Parents can look at our parents page https://kgv.esf.edu.hk/parent/ #KGV_hk #ParentWorkshop #ESFSchools</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/8aa3e3a4613be7c3f9f396b282058ca0.jpg" alt="641253842_1496525152480454_8717358261049782650_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="255">
                        <time>23/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>KGV MUN III is officially in the books!<br><br>Some highlights during the weekend (7-8th of February) at KGV:<br>600+ Participants<br>50+ Schools<br>15 Committees<br>$10,000 donated to FeedingHK (Annual Tradition)<br><br>Congratulations to all delegates! A big congratulations to our most improved award winners, Wu Ka Him Karden and Leung King Hei as the Delegates of the UK in ECOSOC<br><br>A special thank you goes out to our student organisers Rachel, Jacob, Avika, Ariel, Divyam, Dawson, Stephen and Yerim! The Chairs Jason Lu for HRC, Rex Liu for ECOSOC and Amy Wen for WHO.<br><br>#KGVMUN #kgv_hk #ESFSchools #ModelUN #Sustainability #HongKongSchools</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/852621d54e0a22d98775d472687bb3ed.jpg" alt="641336330_1494798409319795_2471012343985533930_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="254">
                        <time>23/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>Wishing you a prosperous Year of the Horse!<br>Happy Lunar New Year to all our students, staff, and families. We hope your celebrations are filled with warmth and quality time with your loved ones. May the year ahead be truly remarkable!<br>#kgv_hk #LNY #ESFSchools #holiday</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/e7e46c7ee8fbda2b6a8ff9df0b8a6597.jpg" alt="640150857_1494628362670133_4454851300925771400_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="253">
                        <time>17/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>Wishing you a prosperous Year of the Horse!<br>Happy Lunar New Year to all our students, staff, and families. We hope your celebrations are filled with warmth and quality time with your loved ones. May the year ahead be truly remarkable!<br>#kgv_hk #LNY #ESFSchools #holiday</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/50285e83986891a8f3cecbd962ee53f3.jpg" alt="631788846_1484453207020982_6481325506145353919_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="252">
                        <time>16/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>Our Lunar New Year Assembly last week was a high-energy celebration of culture and community. From the traditional roar of the Lion Dances to the amazing performances, the hall was filled with festive spirit!<br><br>A shout-out to our student photographer, Stephen, for these stunning highlights. Stephen is usually behind the lens capturing KGV's energy!<br>#kgv_hk #ESFSchools #LNY #assembly</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/c7548891d6fba3f3b121656e0f99f814.jpg" alt="634668379_1488162586650044_2539977019580189542_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="251">
                        <time>13/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>Beyond Remarkable Alumni Series: Stephanie Halim<br><br>Meet our Class of 2018 alumna who is now a researcher at the prestigious Shoulders Lab, MIT. She is currently diving deep into the world of protein folding to uncover how diseases like cancer and viruses evolve.<br><br>From KGV science labs to cutting-edge research in the US, her journey truly embodies what it means to be your own remarkable.<br><br>Swipe to read her interview and learn how KGV prepared her for one of the world’s top research environments! <br>#alumna #kgv_hk #esfschools #beyondremarkable</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/d41cee2704cb6ee2e4d0f511509994c1.jpg" alt="629715797_1483297940469842_1121278024897962166_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="250">
                        <time>12/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>We are proud to celebrate the diverse achievements of our students across academics, athletics, and the arts!<br><br>Alex (Academics): Following his success at the HKU Gifted Talented Program, Alex has been selected for the HKUST IElite program. <br><br>Jacob (Sport): A standout 2025 season in Triathlons! Jacob earned Champion titles in the 2013 Individual and Youth Aquathlon categories, as well as 1st Runner Up in the Youth Duathlon.<br><br>Enoch (Arts): Our talented pianist was recently featured on RTHK, where he performed and spoke about his dedication to the craft.<br>#kgv_hk #ESFSchools #studentspotlights #studentathletics #studentacademics #studentmusician</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/a20c316d6f09f00935eaa2d8de15b50b.jpg" alt="633293021_1484443663688603_1105796651191345261_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="249">
                        <time>11/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>The Food Tech and Chinese Departments joined forces to host a special dumpling-making workshop. Students explored the culinary practice, mastering folding techniques while learning about the traditions that make this so significant. It was a fantastic example of cross-departmental learning in action!<br>#kgv_hk #ESFSchools #foodtech #chinesedept #CNY</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/fb22f6db1ee0b4951d6cedaefa764f71.jpg" alt="630067161_1483565540443082_5803204883193780270_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="248">
                        <time>11/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>To celebrate the arrival of the Year of the Horse, our senior students recently organized a Chinese New Year Festival for our younger school community.<br><br>The event was a perfect blend of fun and education, featuring student-designed games that allowed participants to engage with Chinese culture and language.<br><br>Thank you to all the student organizers for making this such a memorable pre-holiday celebration!<br><br>#kgv_hk #chinesedepartment #ESFSchools #CNY #yearofthehorse</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/c6b9f12541438616e99dcf00bb07d486.jpg" alt="632422068_1483538077112495_4716397203572105070_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="257">
                        <time>27/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>The KGV stage is still cooling down! Last week, 10 student bands performed for an unforgettable night of talent and high energy. <br><br>A massive shout-out to every musician who performed—you guys made it a night to remember! Thank you to the guests for making the atmosphere electric. <br><br>Photo Credits: Huge thanks to student photographer Stephen and Ms. Carlile for capturing these epic moments!<br><br>#kgv_hk #esfschools #studentmusicians #lionrock #battleofthebands #LiveMusic</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/813df42d3801a4308bc4ff9745c4cc8b.jpg" alt="643412954_1498478428951793_5439065282363201229_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="256">
                        <time>25/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>Connecting at KGV. We recently had an insightful parent workshop on emotional resilience! We’re working together to create a harmonious environment for our students at home and at school.  For more information, KGV Parents can look at our parents page https://kgv.esf.edu.hk/parent/ #KGV_hk #ParentWorkshop #ESFSchools</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
